reviewText: great quality, fast service. the games truly were the best choices for best games of the falcons. The service was fast and i received them on time.

This DVD Set includes

Week 3 At New Orleans: Atlanta 27 New Orleans 24
Week 9 vs Tampa Bay: Atlanta 27 Tampa Bay 21
Week 10 vs Baltimore: Atlanta 26 Baltimore 21
This was given as a gift to an Atlanta Falcon fan.....he loves it
Came in time window but was only one disc not three as stated in description. Was only disc 3 no 1 or 2
Theses are all Complete Original Broadcast Games so if you like the Falcons these are 3 great games for your collection.
bought as a gift for a fan
GREAT  DVD ,  WOULD RECOMMEND FOR ANY ATLANTA FALCON FAN , FUN TO WATCH !!!
